    <div class="content">
      <p>Welcome to the Cornucopia Sinatra Project! Stuff anything you like in a cornucopia. To get started, <a href="/signup">sign up</a> or <a href="/login">log in</a> and begin
         stuffing whatever you like into your very own <em>personalized</em> cornucopia. For more information on this Sinatra Project, see the <a href="https://github.com/rstephens5911/cornucopia" target="_blank">README</a>.</p>
      <div class="crud">
        <h5>*links will be active when you log in</h5>
        <br />
        <h3>Cornucopias Controller</h3>
        <br />

        <ul>
          <li><a href=>cornucopias</a>&nbsp show all cornucopias</li>
          <li><a href=>cornucopias/new</a>&nbsp create new cornucopia</li>
          <li><a href=>cornucopias/:id/edit</a>&nbsp update</li>
          <li><a href=>cornucopias/:id</a>&nbsp show one</li>
          <li><a href=>cornucopias/:id/delete</a>&nbsp destroy cornucopia</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Items Controller</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href=>items</a>&nbsp show all items</li>
            <li><a href=>items/new</a>&nbsp create item</li>
            <li><a href=>items/:id/edit</a>&nbsp update</li>
            <li><a href=>items/:id</a>&nbsp show one item</li>
          </ul>

        <h3>Users Controller</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href=>users/:id</a>&nbsp show one user</li>
            <li><a href=>signup</a>&nbsp sign up</li>
            <li><a href=>login</a>&nbsp log in</li>
            <li><a href=>logout</a>&nbsp log out</li>
            <li><a href=>items/:id/delete</a>&nbsp destroy item</li>
          </ul>
          <br>
        </div>
    </div>

